author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Pennantpark Investment reports Qtrly Net Asset Value Per Share of $9.10
text:
February 7, 2018 / 11:33 PM / Updated 7 minutes ago BRIEF-Pennantpark Investment reports Qtrly Net Asset Value Per Share of $9.10 Reuters Staff 
Feb 7 (Reuters) - Pennantpark Investment Corp: 
* PENNANTPARK INVESTMENT CORPORATION ANNOUNCES FINANCIAL RESULTS FOR THE QUARTER ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2017 
* PENNANTPARK INVESTMENT CORP Q1 SALES AND REPAYMENTS OF INVESTMENTS TOTALED $192.3 MILLION 
* PENNANTPARK INVESTMENT - NET INVESTMENT INCOME WAS $14.2 MILLION, FOR THREE MONTHS ENDED DEC 31, 2017 VERSUS $15.0 MILLION FOR THREE MONTHS ENDED DEC 31, 2016‍​ 
* PENNANTPARK INVESTMENT CORP - QTRLY NET ASSET VALUE PER SHARE $9.10 ‍​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
